- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possibility because the paper applies the PLMMSE estimator to the problem of image enhancement from blurred/noisy image pairs. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility because the paper provides a recursive implementation of the estimator and demonstrates its utility in tracking maneuvering targets from position and acceleration measurements. 
- cs.SP (Signal Processing) is also a possibility because the paper deals with signal recovery and filtering.
